<a href="/questions/495849-is-there-any-material-in-this-book-that">Is there any material in this book that would make it inappropriate for a younger reader? Like kissing/intimate scene</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_495849'><a id="like_count_community_question_495849" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/495849?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">6 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F28194.Inkheart">like</a></span>

