  <span id="freeText13186715129049005678" style="display:none">The best fantasy novel, I'ver read.<br />I was too much curious while reading that.<br />I just loved it.<br />The way writer moves the story.<br />Specially,3 ratings for character making.<br />Thanks Cornelia Funke.</span>
