<span id="freeTextContainer7202325067937243618">I have no idea why people like this book. Where is the character developement, the intrigue, the plot? It&apos;s like a lump. After I read it, I thought back and couldn&apos;t even remember the storyline - it was too jumpy and mumbled. Not a good work of fiction.</span>
